                <text><insertwords>Despite <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM331145">clause 12</extref> of Schedule 5 of the Crown Entities Act 2004</citation>,</insertwords> questions arising at a meeting of the Board as to—</text>
                <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
